title: Is wooxy really safe to use
body:
So i know that it doesent affect the game files and its an overlay but i was just wondering why virustotal got this:

https://gyazo.com/b9e84b8ab75f61dd7f78a9c51bc4f156ï»¿

replies.body: It's just a false positive. Wooxy has a callback function that they use for updates, and that's easily mistaken as trojan function. It's a pretty common occurence.
Looks like bad news to me, I would stay faaaarrr away if I was you.
